Performance Director - Based in SingaporeSingapore - 70kGlobal media agency seeks PPC expert to head up a team of 10+ Search Marketing Professionals working on multinational and multimillion accounts.Our client is a market leading Media Agency with a global reputation for innovation and creativity. With annual billing in excess on £150m, a list of famous brands as clients, this is a perfect role for a senior PPC expert to make his mark managing a large team across multiple markets.The RoleHeading up Performance team of 15 peopleDealing with APAC campaignsSenior client management, playing leading role in strategic PPC and wider digital developmentSitting on Senior Management BoardLeading multi-channel pitches and playing key role in business developmentLiaising with local offices throughout APAC and providing expert insight. Monthly travel required The Right Person 6 years+ Search Marketing experienceWorked for an agency previouslyStrong cross-channel knowledgeAbility to identify clients' commercial and marketing needs and objectives for PPCHas managed a large PPC in the pastPlay active role in technology acquisitionAbility to lead pitches and bring in new businessKeen for an exciting move to Singapore The CompanyGlobal Media AgencyStaff of over 1000Singapore APAC officeUK Digital Media team of over 100Amazing benefits (the full works!) Apply now for this fantastic opportunity.
